{
  "title": "Wholesome Italian Orecchiette Oreo Torte",
  "description": "A crowd-pleasing, high-protein-friendly, fatty, and shaggy Italian dish featuring oreo cream biscuits, deglazed, in the form of orecchiettes.",
  "cuisine": "Italian",
